{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PFMJsU5xy9wVUTbgwsXWDo","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Verification Proof: Story 6-2 — Evaluator Verdict JSON Schema & Parsing\n2\t\n3\t**Story:** `_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/6-2-evaluator-verdict-json-schema-parsing.md`\n4\t**Verification Tier:** test-provable\n5\t**Date:** 2026-04-03\n6\t**Verifier:** Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context)\n7\t\n8\t## Build & Test Summary\n9\t\n10\t| Check | Result |\n11\t|-------|--------|\n12\t| `npm run build` | PASS — zero errors, ESM + DTS build succeeded |\n13\t| `npm test` | PASS — 4091 tests passed across 158 test files |\n14\t| `npm run lint` | PASS — 0 errors, 51 warnings (pre-existing, none in verdict-parser) |\n15\t| Coverage (verdict-parser.ts) | 100% Stmts, 91.3% Branch, 100% Funcs, 100% Lines |\n16\t\n17\t## Acceptance Criteria Verification\n18\t\n19\t### AC1: verdict.schema.json exists with correct structure\n20\t**Status:** PASS\n21\t**Evidence:**\n22\t- File exists: `src/schemas/verdict.schema.json` (2062 bytes)\n23\t- Uses `draft-07` (`\"$schema\": \"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"`)\n24\t- Top-level `verdict` enum: `[\"pass\", \"fail\"]`\n25\t- `score` object: `passed`, `failed`, `unknown`, `total` — all `integer` with `minimum: 0`\n26\t- `findings` array: items have `ac` (integer), `description` (string), `status` (enum: pass/fail/unknown), `evidence` object with `commands_run` (array of strings), `output_observed` (string), `reasoning` (string)\n27\t- Optional fields: `evaluator_trace_id` (string), `duration_seconds` (number)\n28\t\n29\t### AC2: Schema validation pass/fail\n30\t**Status:** PASS\n31\t**Evidence:** Tests in `verdict-parser.test.ts` cover:\n32\t- `validates a correct verdict object` — valid verdict passes\n33\t- `rejects missing verdict field` — missing required fields caught\n34\t- `rejects invalid status enum` — bad enum values caught\n35\t- `rejects non-integer score values` — wrong types caught\n36\t-