workflow-engine.ts\n70\t\n71\t### AC7: VerdictParseError class shape\n72\t**Status:** PASS\n73\t**Evidence:**\n74\t- `VerdictParseError extends Error` in verdict-parser.ts (line 47)\n75\t- Fields: `retryable: boolean` (line 48), `rawOutput: string` (line 49), `validationErrors?: string[]` (line 50)\n76\t- Test: `VerdictParseError > extends Error` confirms instanceof check\n77\t- Test: `VerdictParseError > has correct shape` confirms all fields\n78\t\n79\t### AC8: workflow-engine.ts migration\n80\t**Status:** PASS\n81\t**Evidence:**\n82\t- `import { parseVerdict, VerdictParseError } from './verdict-parser.js'` (line 17)\n83\t- `import type { EvaluatorVerdict } from './verdict-parser.js'` (line 18)\n84\t- `export type { EvaluatorVerdict } from './verdict-parser.js'` (line 21) — re-export for backward compat\n85\t- `export { parseVerdict } from './verdict-parser.js'` (line 22) — re-export\n86\t- No inline `interface EvaluatorVerdict` definition found in workflow-engine.ts\n87\t- No inline `function parseVerdict` definition found in workflow-engine.ts\n88\t- All 4091 tests pass — no regressions\n89\t\n90\t### AC9: Unit tests at 80%+ coverage\n91\t**Status:** PASS\n92\t**Evidence:**\n93\t- 33 test lines in `verdict-parser.test.ts` (28 distinct tests per dev notes)\n94\t- Coverage: 100% Stmts, 91.3% Branch, 100% Funcs, 100% Lines (exceeds 80% target)\n95\t- Tests cover: valid parsing, schema validation pass/fail, PASS-without-evidence downgrade, malformed JSON, empty string, partial JSON, extra fields tolerance, VerdictParseError shape, error messages\n96\t\n97\t### AC10: Build succeeds, no regressions\n98\t**Status:** PASS\n99\t**Evidence:**\n100\t- `npm run build`: zero errors, ESM + DTS output generated\n101\t- `npm test`: 4091 passed, 0 failed across 158 test files\n102\t- No regressions in existing workflow-engine test suite\n103\t\n104\t## Final Result\n105\t\n106\t**ALL_PASS (10/10 ACs)**\n107\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"64d7a6a2-a6f8-43cb-b618-df